Class DbDataObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.uni_potsdam.hpi.bpt.bp2014.database.DbObject
      • de.uni_potsdam.hpi.bpt.bp2014.database.DbDataObject
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Connector

    public class DbDataObject
extends DbObject
    This class is the representation of a dataObject in the database. It provides the functionality to retrieve all dataObjects of a scenario as well as their names and startStates.
